                    Edmonton Oilers and Toronto Maple Leafs. Further, I also love Basketball. I am a huge Raptors fan
                    and occasionally play every now and then.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Beyond sports, I really love building mechanical keyboards. The engineering, the customizations you
                    can make, and the little details that go into them makes it thrilling. My career is based around
                    typing on a keyboard, so its nice to have something fun and clicky to work on.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Further, I really love trying new foods, in fact, I'm willing to try anything once. A big fan of hot
                    sauce and spicy food in general. Love music anc going to concerts, festivals, or just jamming out
